VarAttributes.VAR_NOTES: Spaceraft Elapsed Time

Flag to indicate if the local time is synchronized with the RPW DPU clock or not. Possible values: synchronized=0, not synchronized=1. This flag is extracted from ACQUISITION_TIME in L0 packets, it is the MSB of the CUC time.
